cuss the interrelations between the classes of\nPTPIG and TPIG with probe interval graphs and probe proper interval graphs.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 11 Jul 2016 12:42:23 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 23 Jul 2018 17:11:30 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Fri, 27 Jul 2018 12:35:47 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-07-30"}
