\nAGL J2241+4454. This fact, together with the energy dependent sensitivity of\nboth instruments, and the soft spectrum found in the stacking analysis, might\nexplain why AGILE observed the transient events not seen by Fermi/LAT.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 11 Jul 2016 15:44:45 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-10-05"}
